{"tid":1080773,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次去東京 好多地邊想去 唔知點安排 幫幫手","createTime":"2019-03-27T23:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T02:53:00.000Z","uid":101048,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"943ade9bcdca9eae095ed0dda31f4eff69f54d84","tid":1080773,"uid":101048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:39:04.000Z","msg":"下星期就去 點塞d行程好<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 當地時間4點落機 之後去酒店放低野 間酒店係新宿 諗住果晚就係新宿到算<br />\n<br />\nDay2 諗住去河口湖<br />\n<br />\nDay3 想去輕井澤<br />\n<br />\nDay 4/5 未諗到 <br />\n<br />\nDay 6 當地時間 6點上機返香港 <br />\n<br />\n有好多地方想去 想去睇櫻花 有新宿/上野/目黑<br />\n其他地方例外 淺草 台場 池袋 涉谷 原宿 裏原宿 表參道 東京車站 <br />\n<br />\n咁多地方點安排好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb05d6554c19109132ec721c0317e9935bc20ee","tid":1080773,"uid":26675,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:40:45.000Z","msg":"我幫你去埋啦"},{"pid":"119f3c8d55ce422832f997aa20a61e27b284fec5","tid":1080773,"uid":63117,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:44:15.000Z","msg":"day4 青木原樹海"},{"pid":"d3d34ecb5ad2a22532acc140e2d95e73c3fe4e77","tid":1080773,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:47:39.000Z","msg":"One day輕井澤趕到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc51c52890d007813d620c59d83d8808ecfd5041","tid":1080773,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:49:52.000Z","msg":"去遠少少江之島<br />\n真心覺得風景動人<br />\n仲有得睇貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf1d5c32d97f0eb80b255777b71a877af8bfa2e","tid":1080773,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:50:37.000Z","msg":"台場"},{"pid":"2bd5b8ac1db9212eedbab3730af5db8c90a76137","tid":1080773,"uid":119918,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T23:52:00.000Z","msg":"啱啱去完5日，有2日係one day輕并澤同河口湖，奶晒野，邊度都去唔到"},{"pid":"1d5b573c74